@startuml
!pragma useVerticalIf on
hide footbox
title KeibiDrop Session Handshake (v0 - Hybrid PQ + Classical)

actor Alice << Responder >>
participant Relay << Untrusted Server >>
actor Bob << Initiator >>

' === ROOM CREATION ===
Alice -> Alice : Generate ephemeral keys:\n- MLKEM (PK_A1)\n- X25519 (PK_A2)
Alice -> Relay : Register Room:\n{ PKs, Fingerprint, Inbound Port, IP }
Relay -> Alice : OK

' === FINGERPRINT OUT-OF-BAND SHARING ===
Alice -> Bob : Send Fingerprint (via Signal)
Bob -> Alice : Send Fingerprint (via Signal)

' === JOIN FLOW ===
Bob -> Bob : Generate ephemeral keys:\n- MLKEM (PK_B1)\n- X25519 (PK_B2)
Bob -> Relay : Join Room (using Alice’s fingerprint)
Relay -> Bob : { Alice’s PKs, Inbound Port, IP }

Bob -> Bob : Verify Alice's fingerprint == out-of-band
Bob -> Bob : Derive outbound shared secrets:
Bob -> Bob : - Encapsulate: ct_MLKEM = Enc(PK_A1, seed1)
Bob -> Bob : - Encrypt seed2 via X25519 with PK_A2
Bob -> Alice : Send:\n{ PK_Bs, ct_MLKEM, Enc(seed2), IP, Port }

' === ALICE HANDLES BOB'S JOIN ===
Alice -> Alice : Verify Bob’s fingerprint
Alice -> Alice : Derive inbound shared secrets:\n- Decapsulate ct_MLKEM\n- Decrypt seed2
Alice -> Alice : Derive Session Key = HKDF(seed1, seed2)
Alice -> Bob : Encrypted OK

Alice -> Alice : Generate Session Key for Bob
Alice -> Bob : Encrypt and Send session key to Bob

Bob -> Bob : If fingerprint + session key OK\n→ Upgrade to Secure
Bob -> Alice : Encrypted OK

@enduml
